    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Well about using lodash, don't we have it as dependency already?\n\nIt's true, babel does bring us the basics, merge (not deep), all ES5 and ES6 array methods but it's still way lower than lodash I do agree.\n\nStill lodash is HUGE! And I fear that sometimes we can be lazy on the data structure we design because we know we can just use find({prop}, collection), that's another discussion.\n",
